<para style="p">A prayer of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Listen to my plea for justice, Yahweh; pay attention to my call for help!</para>

<para style="q1">Give ear to my prayer from lips without deceit.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Let my vindication come from your presence; let your eyes see what is right!</para>
